data.description: Wonderful new construction home in award winning Chapel Hill ISD. This home would be perfect for first time home buyers. Downstairs offers a spacious living, dining, and kitchen area with tile floors, recessed lighting, and neutral color palette. Fantastic kitchen features granite counter tops, tile back splash, and ample storage space. Adjacent laundry room and pantry is spacious with lots of built-in shelves. Upstairs bedrooms are all a nice size, the full bath has a stunning custom tiled shower. The deck is perfect for enjoying cookouts with friends and family. All of this and more on the half acre lot with mature shade trees. Come see all this wonderful home has to offer. Call for your private tour today!
